The animators really tried to keep the original spirit of the classic shows in this modern incarnation. From the music, to the incidental characters and all the trouble Tom and Jerry got into, we really enjoyed it. It was lots of fun to watch with my son. It was new for both of us. Worth a purchase.
My indication on the video is amount of laughter from the grandkids. My grandchildren love Tom and Jerry and they enjoyed this video.

My granddaughter laughs out loud at these cartoons, and it makes me join in. I remember when my mom and her 4-year-old grand-nephew used to get on the phone and "watch" Tom and Jerry together on television, laughing all the way through. Now I understand why. You can't watch in the company of a child without laughing together. What a fun diversion after spending a day together. And, we can agree to watch just a few at a time and save some for later because each DVD is pretty long. This one has 22 cartoons.
There is nothing better than being in the room when my grandkids watch Tom and Jerry. I love hearing them laugh outloud!
